### [1 Kings (1 Samuel) Chapter 20](../../../bib/kjv/sa1020.htm#001.md)

[1 Kings (1 Samuel)](../../../bib/kjv/sa1001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">sa1 20:0</span></span>

Overview

[Sa1 20:1](../../../bib/kjv/sa1020.htm#001.md), David consults with
Jonathan for his safety; [Sa1 20:11](../../../bib/kjv/sa1020.htm#011.md),
Jonathan and David renew their covenant by oath; [Sa1
20:18](../../../bib/kjv/sa1020.htm#018.md), Jonathan's token to David; [Sa1
20:24](../../../bib/kjv/sa1020.htm#024.md), Saul, missing David, seeks to
kill Jonathan; [Sa1 20:35](../../../bib/kjv/sa1020.htm#035.md), Jonathan
affectionately takes his leave of David.

